com.nokia.sm.net
Class ItemList

java.lang.Object
  com.nokia.sm.net.ItemList

public class ItemList
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements a container for one or more items of different types. An ItemList instance is created empty. Items can be added, replaced, removed and retrieved. Items are accessed by their name. There are convenience methods for retrieving typed items. ItemList instances may contain items that are themselves ItemList instances.
